ED_Title: Extension of the procedure for taking decisions of the General Assembly during the coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) pandemic
ED_DecisionText: On 15 May 2020, the General Assembly, on the proposal of its President (A/74/L.65), decided that its decision 74/544 of 27 March 2020 shall continue to be in effect until the end of June 2020 and that the subsidiary organs of the Assembly might apply the procedure set out in decision 74/544.
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the resumed part of the session will be contained in the official record of the GA (A/74/49 (Vol. III)) after editorial review.
